articles.description: A high-profile appointment, Baird will take over as Cricket Australia boss in February after Lachlan Henderson steps down due to work commitments.
articles.content:
Former NSW premier Mike Baird has been appointed as the new chair of Cricket Australia (CA).
  • Baird will take on the role from next February
  • He was NSW premier between 2014 and 2017
